cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV

The paper discusses a reinforcement learning technique for directed exploration, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of function approximation also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG). The focus on exploration and visit-counters relates to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the demonstration of the approach on Atari games suggests a connection to computer vision (cs.CV).
